{"tid":2390312,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣港式黃店-啡竇","createTime":"2021-02-01T12:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T19:41:25.000Z","uid":182683,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a47bfa704f20aafdd2719751bfe6b09eacdf5b4d","tid":2390312,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:50:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GpnkVQk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGpnkVQk.jpg&h=250a24d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台妹：支持香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣黃店！啡竇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n間野開係鳳山區啲巷仔 都幾隱蔽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似香港人開的 半個餐單都是香港野 細細間咖啡室 坐得幾c服～ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲野食正常 冇咩大驚喜 個蛋撻唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣好似好難入口到香港既材料去整野食 整唔到100%香港味都冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家遲下去旅行可以幫襯下 身處台灣開鋪貼哂文宣唔係冇風險 大可以賣香港野但唔表態 照做到生意 多謝佢地！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w1ub2ws.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw1ub2ws.jpg&h=6eb92a80&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mff29bt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMff29bt.jpg&h=74eb927e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YUgayC9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYUgayC9.jpg&h=721711de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPBefRu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPBefRu.jpg&h=fe25edfd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gfndwpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgfndwpQ.jpg&h=4e6c6072&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPNXX4R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPNXX4R.jpg&h=2aaedd0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HAKLnww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHAKLnww.jpg&h=279f8fb1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aBvq6Yc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaBvq6Yc.jpg&h=881ef54a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIg有片有興趣可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nIg:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkfoodghost%2F&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQlzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=5b68fb3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkfoodghost/</a><br />\nMeWe:<a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/hkfoodghost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2Fhkfoodghost&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQlzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=14905dc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/hkfoodghost</a><br />\n食譜就呢到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQlzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=1f1cac24\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/channel/UCqRF5PLGsAWPGjluK1DoBNw</a>"},{"pid":"6959f2742caa47d2d3e841a963bc70fc00aedab0","tid":2390312,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:51:50.000Z","msg":"冇台妹ig<br />\n拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e6c243beb4e1f90d5752733f144029de3ad8f8","tid":2390312,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6959f2742caa47d2d3e841a963bc70fc00aedab0","tid":2390312,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T12:51:50.000Z","msg":"冇台妹ig<br />\n拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T13:00: